latestIgtvVideos.caption: This will be my last IG post for a while. I’m taking some time off to breath and to work on myself. Tomorrow is my and my nephew’s birthdays and as you may assume it will be a very emotional day for me and my family. I’m asking if you were planning to send gifts flowers or even just birthday wishes please hold on to it until we’ve had a chance to heal more. I will be back soon LOVE YOU ALL ❤️
I woke up to this….. so blessed and so grateful for my life. Thank you @dolcegabbana @luciodirosa  @siqueiragui for inviting to this magnificent place!!!
Still not over this moment….. thank you everyone who came out especially my friends @drayamichele @jaimexie @dashaunwesley  and thank you @patron @herveleger @christianjuulnielsen
